metadata.name: Bad Influence #735
metadata.description:
To the misfits, rebels and renegades out there. To the ones who refuse to fall in line. To those who dare to break down barriers and go against the grain. Welcome to Bad Influence -- a brand that stands for Wild Originality.

After the initial sale:
~40% of supply auctioned, one per day, for ~10 years as we build a decentralised studio with tentacles in art, entertainment, fashion, gaming and beyond.
~20% of supply to be awarded gradually on merit to the growing band of talent and creators needed to make the dream reality.
